(BERNADETTE enters the walk-in and after a moment emerges silently shrieking. Seeing Task through the office window, SHE gets his attention. SHE points at him and then herself and then the walk-in in her panic. TASK thinks she is making advances toward him and asking him to meet her in the walk-in. HE blows kisses back to her. SHE throws her chefs hat down in frustration and tears off her apron. TASK sees only a woman mad with passion and begins to tear his own clothes off. BERNADETTE pulls the body out of the walk-in and points to it but TASK is trying to get his shirt off over his helmet and doesn't see a thing. Fed up, BERNADETTE runs into the dining room. TASK, finally undressed, emerges from the office in his underwear.)


